title: Hour 2 - Antoine Walker

description:
In hour 2, Antoine Walker joins to talk the possibility of Kevin Durant going back to Golden State. USC and UCLA are leaving the PAC 12, USC has been unhappy for awhile. Aaron Rodgers now needs a #1 WR, Davante Adams may've won the trade.
